132
00:07:07,570 --> 00:07:09,370
I'm very sorry.

133
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:12,770
We already informed you of that the other day.

134
00:07:12,770 --> 00:07:14,270
Due to careless oversight on our part,

135
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:16,370
