141
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:26,670
Who the heck came in between and took the room?

142
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:29,870
It's me over here.

143
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:32,370
Well, I'm so very sorry.

144
00:07:32,370 --> 00:07:36,770
My daughter happens to be friends with the owner of this train.

145
00:07:36,770 --> 00:07:40,370
Well, no need for worry since I am on board.

146
00:07:40,370 --> 00:07:43,970
